⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of The Elden Ring
node ER · ER · ⟦The Elden Ring:ER:972b3b⟧

WHO   — The Elden Ring — the Order itself, shattered
WHAT  — The vessel of Order itself — the great runic ring whose composition decides the laws of the world.
WHERE — ER · Elden Ring  Framework inputs: the frame  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Shattered, its Great Runes drove the demigods mad and ignited the Shattering; mending or remaking it is the entire quest and the meaning of every ending.
HOW   — Formed from the Elden Beast sent by the Greater Will, held within the Erdtree and within Marika; its runes define what the world is.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  The law of the world, broken into shards — and every ending is a choice of what to write back into it.

